  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] Reveal the top 4 cards of your deck. Add 1 [Four
    Great Dragons] trait or 1 yellow card among them to the hand. Return the rest
    to the bottom of the deck. Then, place this card in the battle area.[Main] <Delay>Place
    1 [Trial of the Four Great Dragons] from your hand in the battle area, or you
    may trash 1 [Four Great Dragons] trait card in your hand. If you did either,
    1 of your opponent''s Digimon gets -7000 DP for the turn.'
